# Change log for samba-exporter package

## Version 0.5

- Bugfix
  - Stabilizes the pipe communication, see https://github.com/imker25/samba_exporter/issues/17 
- Features
  - Add `-request-timeout` option to samba_exporter
  - Add example configurations for grafana and prometheus

## Version 0.4

- Features
  - Enhanced metrics
  - Enhanced logging for type conversion errors
- Internal enhancements
  - Adapt folder structure for compatibility to go tools and VS Code plugins
